  "name": "Withering Coils",
  "ownership": {
    "default": 0
  },
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create three spectral coils gleaming with green necrotic energy. Make a <strong>ranged spell attack</strong> against up to three separate targets within range, one for each coil. On a hit, the coil deals <strong>3d12 necrotic damage</strong>, and the target must succeed on a <strong>Wisdom saving throw</strong> or become frightened of you until the end of your next turn. A creature hit with multiple coils makes only one <strong>Wisdom saving throw</strong>.</p><p><strong><em>At Higher Levels:</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 5th level or higher, you can create one additional coil for each slot level above 4th.</p>",
